  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5e28c2e20bb6c4240a55d8edffb777ec, type: 3}
  m_Name: Darry'sHouseInside
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NewDialogueData
  npcName: Chime
  dialogueLines:
  - LineID: Start
    Speaker: Chime
    text: There's a dangerous entity in the house trying to get to Darry.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part II
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part II
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Move objects in the house around to block the entity and make a path Darry
      can use to escape.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part III
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part III
    Speaker: Chime
    text: If the entity gets too close, you can briefly possess them by pressing
      RT / RMB while looking in their direction, and make them go a different direction.
      They will fight your influence, though.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 1
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
